"title": "4019: life, believers' experience of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4019",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is at work in all that happens to believers, whether to warn them, to draw them to himself or to do them good.</p>\n<h2>God has a purpose in all the experiences that believers have in life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:22\">GEN 21:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:16\">GEN 28:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:20-Gen39:21\">GEN 39:20–39:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:5-Gen45:8\">GEN 45:5–45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:6-1Sam2:9\">1SA 2:6–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11-1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:11–29:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:10-Job42:13\">JOB 42:10–42:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:6-Ps75:7\">PSA 75:6–75:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:28\">ACT 17:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12\">1PE 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of this conviction leads to despair</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:1-Eccl1:2\">ECC 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:16-Eccl1:17\">ECC 1:16–1:17</a></p>\n<h2>God uses every experience in the lives of believers for good</h2>\n<h3>To warn and correct</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:67\">PSA 119:67</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:17\">GEN 12:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:13-2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:13–7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:17\">JOB 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:17\">ISA 38:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:9-Isa48:10\">ISA 48:9–48:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:10-Amos4:11\">AMO 4:10–4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5-Heb12:11\">HEB 12:5–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">REV 9:20–9:21</a></p>\n<h3>To test and exercise believers' trust in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:15-Deut8:16\">DEU 8:15–8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:22-Exod15:25\">EXO 15:22–15:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:21-Judg2:22\">JDG 2:21–2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:6\">PSA 23:1–23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:7\">PSA 81:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:1-Isa43:2\">ISA 43:1–43:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:35-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:35–8:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:12\">PHP 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:17-Heb11:19\">HEB 11:17–11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a></p>\n<h3>To purify and prepare believers for glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16-2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:16–4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:10\">JOB 23:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:10\">PSA 66:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:10\">ISA 48:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:7\">JER 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech13:8-Zech13:9\">ZEC 13:8–13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:3-Rom5:5\">ROM 5:3–5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:30\">ROM 8:28–8:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6-1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:6–1:7</a></p>\n<h3>To benefit others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:14\">EST 4:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:6\">2CO 1:3–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:15\">2CO 4:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:12-Phil1:14\">PHP 1:12–1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:10\">2TI 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>In all of life's experiences believers should be thankful and trusting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:6\">PHP 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">GEN 8:20</a> <em>Noah's sacrifice would, among other things, express his thankfulness</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:20-Job1:21\">JOB 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:1-Ps103:2\">PSA 103:1–103:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:25\">ACT 16:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:20\">EPH 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:4-1Tim4:5\">1TI 4:4–4:5</a></p>\n<h2>Believers do not merit the blessings they receive</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:10\">PSA 103:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:10\">GEN 32:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:19-Gen50:21\">GEN 50:19–50:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:13\">EZR 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22\">LAM 3:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:6\">LUK 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:23\">ROM 6:23</a></p>",
